node.text:
Rainbow Island, Iran 🇮🇷 The soil composing Hormuz Island in #Iran is highly concentrated with Iron Oxide. This concentration leads to red coloration, which is washed up in the waves.
Have you ever seen anything like this?

📽 @elhamgholami #nature
📍 Hormuz, Iran

node.text:
How incredible is Siwa Oasis in Egypt? 🇪🇬 💙 "Siwa lakes are considered to have healing properties for sinus, skin, and eye conditions, which have allowed the oasis to be promoted as a medical and recreational destination. The water here has a salt concentration of more than 95%."

📽 @flyyestguy #nature
📍 Siwa Oasis, Egypt
🎶 Egyptian Pools - Jinsang

node.text:
How sweet are these guinea pigs enjoying a rainy day? 🥺 These footage via @titorenogpigs shows Guinea pigs or domestic guinea pig, also known as the cavy or domestic cavy are small, sociable, 'chatty' rodents. There are different breeds and varieties of guinea pigs, with a wide variety of colour and coat lengths.
Typically live for 5-6 years, but some may live longer.
Traditionally thought of as good first pets for children, but it should always be an adult that takes responsibility to ensure they are properly handled and cared for.

📽 @titorenogpigs #nature

node.text:
Welcome to paradise at Calilo, a tranquil retreat via @adrianbaias with @florina__toma - a visionary conservation project that offers an escape from the clamour and the crowds. Think sun-drenched seclusion surrounded by an ancient olive-pricked landscape - @nature and art at its heart. Find yourself and all you need in a land in deep connection with everything.

Who would you share this hideout with? 😌

📽 @adrianbaias w/ @florina__toma #nature
📍 Calilo Hotel, Ios, Greece
🎶 Henry Mancini - Lujon

node.text:
Can’t stop watching this!@carlweiseth and @ianjesr are the best at paragliding proximity flying. Just insanely good 🤯

“Proximity flying” is the practice of flying a paragliding close to the faces and ridges of mountains. Flying near terrain gives a greater sense of speed due to having a close visual reference. Isn't it? 🤙 

🪂 @carlweiseth
📽 @ianjesr #nature
📍Salt Lake City, Utah

Have you ever seen @nature hummocks? The wonderland of Puga Valley in Ladakh, India via @apytravelstories will left you speechless 🤯 If you are a @nature lover, then you should really visit this place. It's incredible landscape attracts the visitors.

The Puga valley in the Changthang valley lies at about 22 km to the east of the Salt Lake valley across the Polokonka La pass (5,350 m). It is famous for its borax and sulphur deposits and hot water springs.
